	(text_box "!!! CAUTION !!!\n\nVDD3 must remain between 2.5V and 5.5V.\n\nThe switchable analog voltage range is from 0V to VDD3. The maximum switchable current is 100mA, and the on-resistance (Ron) varies between 65Ω at lower supply voltages and 15Ω at higher supply voltages."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
